<h2 class='section' id='lets_keep_moving_the_web_forward'>Let&#8217;s keep moving the web forward</h2>

<p>origin was built with ease-of-use in mind &#8211; bringing the best conventions from front to backend into a single Sinatra project. Use it if you like, move along if you don&#8217;t.</p>

